div.font: Image all vectors are in two-dimensional space. They point to different directions,
meaning they look different to the machine and thus the machine can know
them separately. The dot multiplication between queries and keys indicates
how much attention a token should pay to another because the dot mutip. result is
larger if two vectors have more similar pointing directions, and vice versa.
